## Next Steps

1. **Verify scope** — Determine if your system is high-risk under Annex III before completing documentation. Articles 9-15 only apply to high-risk systems. Consult Section 0 above and seek legal review
2. Complete all `[MANUAL INPUT REQUIRED]` fields in the Annex IV sections
3. Run `aitrace audit` with production traces for Article 12 trace field coverage scoring
4. Verify PII classifications — flows marked "likely" need DPIA
5. Add GDPR Article 6 legal basis for each processing activity
6. Draft Data Processing Agreements (Article 28) for each "processor" service
7. Set data retention periods: providers must retain for 10 years (Article 18), deployers for at least 6 months (Article 26(5))
8. Store this package in version control — Article 11 requires it to be kept current
9. Have the package reviewed by a legal/compliance professional

